<!-- wp:paragraph {"className":"has-text-color world-intro","style":{"typography":{"fontSize":"var(\u002d\u002dwp\u002d\u002dpreset\u002d\u002dfont-size\u002d\u002dxl)","textAlign":"center"},"color":{"text":"var(\u002d\u002dwp\u002d\u002dpreset\u002d\u002dcolor\u002d\u002dc-ash)"}}} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center has-text-color world-intro" style="color:var(--wp--preset--color--c-ash);font-size:var(--wp--preset--font-size--xl)">A realm woven from shadow and starlight, where ancient powers stir beneath crumbling kingdoms and the boundary between life and oblivion frays with every passing age.</p>
